Additional details

Product description

Power supply: 85-250V AC
Max. Current: 3000W 16A
Wireless Standard: Wi-Fi 2.4GHz b/g/n
Security Mechanism: WEP/WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK
Operating Temp: -20~70 °C
Material: RF-ABS
Size:9.4*5.7*3.3cm
Connector: Universal
Include waterproof temperature sensor DS18B20,probe:stainless steel temperature probe ,measuring range:-55~125 °C,opeating voltage:3.0-5.5V,length 1m
Functions:

Remote ON/OFF: Turn electrical devices on/off from anywhere,when the temperature of enviroment fall within the rang,it will automatically turn on/off appliance ans support presetting range of temperature,you can also monitor daily power consumption in real time by tuya smart life app
Network Support: Control electrical devices over Wi-Fi or 2/3/4G mobile network
Voice Control: Works perfectly with Amazon Alexa
Extra bluetooth and RF function,default wifi remote,once configured with tuya app,if the device is offline,you can control it with phone bluetooth by tuya app in available distance,support fixed code 433Mhz RFTips:
MHCOZY Smart wifi switch only support 2.4G WIFI router and 2/3/4G mobile network, 5G router is not available.When pairing,please put the switch close to your router.
Please do not exceed the maximum load current of 16A
Package Included

1pcs16A WIFI Wireless smart switch*1pcs 1m waterproof DS18B20 temperature probe sesnor cable
1*Instruction
